title: Google\Analytics\Data\V1beta\Row
name: Row
description:
Report data for each row.

For example if RunReportRequest contains:

"dimensions": [
  {
    "name": "eventName"
  },
  {
    "name": "countryId"
  }
],
"metrics": [
  {
    "name": "eventCount"
  }
]

One row with 'in_app_purchase' as the eventName, 'JP' as the countryId, and 15 as the eventCount, would be:

"dimensionValues": [
  {
    "value": "in_app_purchase"
  },
  {
    "value": "JP"
  }
],
"metricValues": [
  {
    "value": "15"
  }
]

Generated from protobuf message google.analytics.data.v1beta.Row

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message
